snippet.title: Deepsea Salvor - Early Access Trailer
snippet.description:
Deepsea Salvor is an action roguelike made by one guy. It has over 100 unique powerups designed to change the way you play the game! It has enemies with randomized abilities to challenge you every time! It has thousands of battle arena variants to navigate wisely! Out now on Steam Early Access.

https://store.steampowered.com/app/1059640/Deepsea_Salvor/

https://twitter.com/DeepseaSalvor

Music is Zero Zero Zero by Alexandr Zhelanov
Track licensed under free licence of Creative Commons CC BY 4.0.
https://www.youtube.com/watch?v=Ck7Ax-Xdh-c
